###########################


Description
+++++++++++

This model is used to test whether each synapse
uses exactly one buffer

Here the AMPA synapse uses one buffer: spikesAMPA
but the AMPA_NMDA synapse uses two buffers: spikesExc and spikesAMPA

Negative case.


